// ====== Ø¬Ù„Ø¨ Ùˆ Ø¹Ø±Ø¶ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ù‚Ø§Ù„Ø§Øª Ù…Ù† ÙØ§ÙŠØ±Ø¨ÙŠØ² ======
async function fetchArticles() {
  const q = query(collection(db, "articles"), orderBy("timestamp", "desc"));
  const snapshot = await getDocs(q);
  articles = [];
  snapshot.forEach(docSnap => {
    const data = docSnap.data();
    articles.push({...data, id: docSnap.id});
  });
  renderFeatured();
  renderArticles();
  renderTags();
}

// ======= Ø¹Ø±Ø¶ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ù‚Ø§Ù„Ø§Øª Ø§Ù„Ù…Ù…ÙŠØ²Ø© =======
function renderFeatured() {
  const featuredSlider = document.getElementById('featuredSlider');
  featuredSlider.innerHTML = '';
  articles.filter(a => a.featured).forEach(article => {
    const card = document.createElement('div');
    card.className = 'featured-card';
    card.innerHTML = `
      <div class="featured-card-content">
        <div class="featured-card-title">${article.title}</div>
        <div class="featured-card-tags">${(article.tags||[]).map(tag => <span class="tag">${tag.trim()}</span>).join('')}</div>
      </div>
    `;
    card.onclick = () => viewArticle(article.id);
    featuredSlider.appendChild(card);
  });
}

// ======= Ø¹Ø±Ø¶ Ø§Ù„ÙÙ„Ø§ØªØ± (Ø§Ù„ÙˆØ³ÙˆÙ…) =======
function renderTags() {
  const tagFilter = document.getElementById('tagFilter');
  let tagsSet = new Set();
  articles.forEach(a => (a.tags||[]).forEach(tag => tagsSet.add(tag.trim())));
  let tagsArr = Array.from(tagsSet);
  if (tagsArr.length == 0) {
    tagFilter.innerHTML = '';
    selectedTags.clear();
    return;
  }
  tagFilter.innerHTML = tagsArr.map(tag => 
    <button class="tag-button${selectedTags.has(tag)?' active':''}" onclick="handleTagClick('${tag}')">${tag}</button>
  ).join('');
}

// ======= Ø¹Ù†Ø¯ Ø§Ù„Ø¶ØºØ· Ø¹Ù„Ù‰ ÙˆØ³Ù… (Ù„Ù„ØªØµÙÙŠØ©) =======
window.handleTagClick = function(tag) {
  if (selectedTags.has(tag)) selectedTags.delete(tag);
  else selectedTags.add(tag);
  renderTags();
  renderArticles();
}

// ======= Ø¹Ø±Ø¶ Ø´Ø¨ÙƒØ© Ø§Ù„Ù…Ù‚Ø§Ù„Ø§Øª =======
function renderArticles() {
  const grid = document.getElementById('articlesGrid');
  grid.innerHTML = '';
  let toShow = articles.filter(article => {
    if (selectedTags.size == 0) return true;
    return (article.tags||[]).some(tag => selectedTags.has(tag.trim()));
  });
  if (toShow.length==0) {
    grid.innerHTML = '<div>Ù„Ø§ ØªÙˆØ¬Ø¯ Ù…Ù‚Ø§Ù„Ø§Øª Ø­Ø§Ù„ÙŠØ§Ù‹ Ù„Ù‡Ø°Ù‡ Ø§Ù„ÙØ¦Ø©.</div>';
    return;
  }
  toShow.forEach(article => {
    const card = document.createElement('div');
    card.className = 'article-card';
    card.innerHTML = `
      <div class="article-image">${article.img?<img src="${article.img}" />: 'ğŸ“„'}</div>
      <div class="article-content">
        <div class="article-title">${article.title}</div>
        <div class="article-excerpt">${article.content.slice(0,90)}...</div>
        <div class="article-meta">
          <span>${(article.tags||[]).join(', ')}</span>
          <span>${new Date(article.timestamp).toLocaleDateString('ar-EG')}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    `;
    card.onclick = () => viewArticle(article.id);
    grid.appendChild(card);
  });
}

// ======= ÙØªØ­ ØªÙØ§ØµÙŠÙ„ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ù‚Ø§Ù„Ø© =======
function viewArticle(aid) {
  const article = articles.find(a => a.id===aid);
  if (!article) return;
  const detail = document.getElementById('articleDetail');
  detail.classList.add('active');
  detail.scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'});
  detail.innerHTML = `
    <button class="btn-secondary back-button" onclick="closeArticleDetail()">Ø¹ÙˆØ¯Ø© Ù„Ù„Ù…Ù‚Ø§Ù„Ø§Øª</button>
    ${article.img?<img src="${article.img}" />:''}
    <div class="article-detail-title">${article.title}</div>
    <div class="article-detail-meta">${(article.tags||[]).join('ØŒ ')} | ${new Date(article.timestamp).toLocaleDateString('ar-EG')}</div>
    <div class="article-detail-content">${article.content.replace(/\n/g,'<br>')}</div>
    <div class="share-buttons">
      <button class="share-btn" onclick="shareArticle('${article.title}','${location.href}')">Ù…Ø´Ø§Ø±ÙƒØ© ğŸŒ</button>
    </div>
  `;
  document.getElementById('articlesGrid').classList.add('hidden');
  document.getElementById('featuredSlider').parentElement.classList.add('hidden');
  document.getElementById('tagFilter').classList.add('hidden');
}
window.closeArticleDetail = function() {
  document.getElementById('articleDetail').classList.remove('active');
  document.getElementById('articlesGrid').classList.remove('hidden');
  document.getElementById('featuredSlider').parentElement.classList.remove('hidden');
  document.getElementById('tagFilter').classList.remove('hidden');
}
window.shareArticle = function(title, url) {
  if (navigator.share) {
    navigator.share({title, url});
  } else {
    navigator.clipboard.writeText(url);
    alert('ØªÙ… Ù†Ø³Ø® Ø±Ø§Ø¨Ø· Ø§Ù„Ù…Ù‚Ø§Ù„Ø©!');
  }
}

// ============= Ù„ÙˆØ­Ø© Ø§Ù„Ø¥Ø¯Ø§Ø±Ø©: Ø¥Ø¶Ø§ÙØ© Ù…Ù‚Ø§Ù„ =============
window.handleAddArticle = async function(e) {
  e.preventDefault();
  if (!isAdminLoggedIn) return;
  const title = document.getElementById('articleTitle').value.trim();
  const content = document.getElementById('articleContent').value.trim();
  const tags = document.getElementById('articleTags').value.split(',').map(t=>t.trim()).filter(t=>t);
  const featured = document.getElementById('articleFeatured').checked;
  const timestamp = Date.now();
  let img = '';
  const imgFile = document.getElementById('articleImage').files[0];
  if(imgFile){
    img = await readAsDataURL(imgFile);
  }
  await addDoc(collection(db, "articles"), { title, content, tags, featured, timestamp, img });
  fetchArticles();
  resetForm();
}
function readAsDataURL(file){
  return new Promise(resolve => {
    const reader = new FileReader();
    reader.onload = e => resolve(e.target.result);
    reader.readAsDataURL(file);
  });
}
function resetForm(){
  document.getElementById('articleTitle').value = '';
  document.getElementById('articleContent').value = '';
  document.getElementById('articleTags').value = '';
  document.getElementById('articleFeatured').checked = false;
  document.getElementById('articleImage').value = '';
}

